Saurin karuwar cutar coronavirus (COVID-19) a cikin Tarayyar Turai/Yankin Tattalin Arzikin Turai da Ingila, daga 1 ga Janairu zuwa 15 ga Maris, 2020
Kasuwancin cutar coronavirus (COVID-19) na nuna irin wannan yanayin a cikin ƙasashen Tarayyar Turai / Yankin Tattalin Arzikin Turai da Burtaniya wanda ke tabbatar da cewa, yayin da a wani mataki daban-daban dangane da ƙasa, cutar COVID-19 tana ci gaba da sauri a duk ƙasashe.
Dangane da gogewar Italiya, ƙasashe, asibitoci da raka'a masu kulawa mai tsanani ya kamata su kara shirye-shiryen su don karuwar marasa lafiya da ke fama da COVID-19 waɗanda za su buƙaci kula da lafiya, musamman ma kula da gaggawa.
A ranar 31 ga Disamba, 2019, an ruwaito wani rukuni na cututtukan huhu na rashin sani a Wuhan, lardin Hubei, China.
A ranar 9 ga Janairu, 2020, Cibiyar Kula da Cututtuka da Rigakafin Cututtuka ta kasar Sin ta ba da rahoton cewa mai haifar da cutar shine sabon coronavirus wanda yanzu ake kira mawuyacin cututtukan numfashi na coronavirus 2 (SARS-CoV-2).
Tun daga wannan lokacin, cutar da ta haifar da kamuwa da cutar SARS-CoV-2 an kira ta cutar coronavirus (COVID-19).
Shaidar zuwa yau ita ce kusan 80% na mutanen da ke da COVID-19 suna da wata cuta mai sauƙi, watau kamuwa da cutar tasowa tare da ko ba tare da cutar huhu ba, kuma yawancin waɗannan suna murmurewa.
A kusan kashi 14% na shari'o'in, COVID-19 ya zama mummunan cuta wanda ke buƙatar asibiti yayin da sauran 6% na shari'o'in ke fuskantar mummunan cuta da ke buƙatar kulawa mai tsanani.
Yawan marasa lafiya da aka kwantar a asibiti saboda COVID-19 kusan kashi 4 ne.
A cikin wannan binciken, mun kimanta yanayin yawan kamuwa da COVID-19 a kowace ƙasa ta Tarayyar Turai / Yankin Tattalin Arzikin Turai (EU / EEA) da Burtaniya (UK) kuma mun kwatanta su da na lardin Hubei, China.
Mun kuma kwatanta adadin shari'o'in COVID-19 na yanzu a cikin ƙasashen EU / EEA da Burtaniya da na Italiya a ranar 31 ga Janairu15 ga Maris 2020.
Maganganun COVID-19 a ƙasashen EU / EEA da Burtaniya
Bayan China, COVID-19 ta ci gaba da yaduwar ƙasa kuma motsin zuciyar cutar COVID-19 a sauran duniya a halin yanzu yana bin wannan ƙasar.
A ranar 11 ga Maris, 2020, Babban Daraktan Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya (WHO) ya ayyana COVID-19 a matsayin annoba.
A cikin batun 5 ga Maris na Eurosurveillance 2020, Spiteri et al. sun ba da rahoton farkon mutanen Turai da aka tabbatar da cutar COVID-19 bisa ga ma'anar yanayin WHO.
A cikin EU/EEA, Faransa ta ba da rahoton farkon cututtuka uku na farko a ranar 24 ga Janairu 2020 a cikin mutanen da suka dawo daga Wuhan, lardin Hubei, China.
Ya zuwa 15 ga Maris, 2020, an gano shari'o'in COVID-19 a duk ƙasashen EU / EEA 30 da Burtaniya (UK), wanda tsakanin 31 ga Disamba, 2019 zuwa wannan ranar, an ba da rahoton shari'o'i 39,768 da mutuwar 1,727, tare da shari'o'i 17,750 da mutuwar 1,441 daga Italiya kawai.
Samun adadin da aka samu na kamuwa da cutar COVID-19
A Cibiyar Tarayya ta Turai don Rigakafin Cututtuka da Kulawa (ECDC), an sabunta adadin shari'o'in COVID-19 da aka sanar a kowace ƙasa a duniya, wanda aka samo daga tushe na hukuma kawai kamar su ƙasashe  Ma'aikatar Lafiya, hukumomin kiwon lafiya na ƙasa da na yanki da WHO, kowace rana a karfe 8:00 na safe.
An yi amfani da waɗannan bayanan don kimanta yanayin COVID-19 a cikin EU / EEA da Burtaniya, da kuma kwatanta su da na Italiya.
A matsayin wakilcin yaduwar shari'o'in COVID-19 masu aiki, mun lissafa raguwar kwanaki 14 na yawan cututtukan COVID-19, don haka muna la'akari da yanayin yanayin COVID-19, a kowace ƙasar EU / EEA da Burtaniya, a lokacin 1 ga Janairu zuwa 15 ga Maris 2020.
Mun kuma gabatar da jimlar adadin shari'o'in da aka sanar a kowace ƙasa a ranar 15 ga Maris, 2020 da karfe 8:00 na safe idan aka kwatanta da na Italiya don lokacin 31 ga Janairu15 ga Maris, 2020.
Hanyoyin COVID-19 a ƙasashen EU / EEA da Burtaniya
Hanyoyin da aka rage yawan cututtukan COVID-19 na kwanaki 14 a cikin ƙasashen EU / EEA da Burtaniya gabaɗaya sun bi na lardin Hubei (China) (Figure 1).
Ga EU/EEA da Burtaniya gabaɗaya, jimlar cutar COVID-19 ta fara ƙaruwa a kusa da ranar 21 ga Fabrairu sannan ta ƙaru sosai a kusa da ranar 28 ga Fabrairu 2020 (Kayan ƙarin).
Wannan yafi haifar da saurin karuwar adadin shari'o'in da aka ruwaito daga Italiya, amma duk sauran ƙasashen EU / EEA da Burtaniya sun nuna irin wannan haɓaka yanayin yawan cutar COVID-19 (Kayan kari).
Hoton 2 ya nuna jimlar adadin masu kamuwa da COVID-19, a cikin ƙasashen EU / EEA da Burtaniya idan aka kwatanta da na Italiya a cikin 31 Janairu15 Maris 2020.
Ya nuna cewa, a ranar 15 ga Maris da karfe 8:00 na safe, wasu ƙasashen EU/EEA 15 da Birtaniya sun riga sun ba da rahoton adadin adadin shari'o'i da aka kwatanta da na Italiya makonni 3 kawai da suka gabata ko kuma ƙasa da haka.
Sakamakonmu ya nuna cewa adadin mutanen da aka sanar da cutar COVID-19 suna ƙaruwa cikin sauri a cikin EU / EEA da Burtaniya.
Hanyoyin da aka lura a cikin yawan cutar COVID-19 sun nuna cewa annobar tana ci gaba da sauri a duk ƙasashe.
Wannan duk da cewa kasashe suna cikin matakai daban-daban, bambance-bambance a cikin martani na lafiyar jama'a na ƙasa, kuma wataƙila ma'anar shari'o'i daban-daban a cikin ƙasashe da ladabi daban-daban don zaɓar marasa lafiya waɗanda dole ne a gwada su don tabbatar da COVID-19, gami da gwajin kamawa.
A farkon Maris 2020, likitoci a yankunan da cutar ta shafa na Italiya sun bayyana halin da ake ciki inda kusan kashi 10% na marasa lafiya da ke fama da COVID-19 ke buƙatar kulawa mai tsanani kuma kafofin watsa labarai sun ba da rahoton cewa asibitoci da raka'a masu kulawa mai tsanani a waɗannan yankuna sun riga sun kai iyakar ƙarfin su.
Bayanai game da shigar da shari'o'in COVID-19 a asibiti da/ko na'urar kulawa mai tsanani a halin yanzu suna samuwa a matakin EU / EEA don kashi 6% da 1% na shari'o'in, bi da bi (ba a nuna bayanai ba).
Duk da haka, ya kamata a tattara su a cikin tsari don a cika bayanan sa ido na yanzu wanda ke mai da hankali kan yawan shari'o'in da aka ruwaito da kuma yawan mutuwar.
Wani binciken da aka gudanar a 201011 ya nuna bambancin da ke tsakanin wuraren da ake kula da marasa lafiya a Turai, daga 29.2 a Jamus zuwa 4.2 a kowace 100,000 a Portugal.
Wannan yana nufin cewa ƙasashe na iya samun albarkatu fiye da Italiya (12.5 wuraren kula da gaggawa da wuraren kula da matsakaici a kowace 100,000 mutane a 201011).
Ana ba da yanayin samfurin da ya shafi ƙoshin lafiyar lafiyar, tare da kimantawa ga kowace ƙasa ta EU / EEA da Burtaniya na yaduwar shari'o'in COVID-19 da aka kwantar a asibiti tare da haɗarin 90% na wucewa ƙarfin gado na kulawa mai tsanani, a cikin sabuntawa ta shida na ECDC mai saurin kimanta haɗari akan COVID-19.
Tun da har yanzu akwai wasu cututtuka a wasu yankuna a cikin kasashen EU/EEA da Birtaniya, kuma asibitoci da wuraren kula da gaggawa sukan yi wa wani yanki da aka ƙayyade yawan mutanen da ke cikin wuraren kula da gaggawa, ya kamata a ba da bayani game da cututtuka da wuraren kula da gaggawa a Nomenclature na yankunan yankuna don kididdiga 2 (NUTS-2).
Kwarewar Italiya da yanayin yanzu a wasu ƙasashe sun nuna cewa annobar COVID-19 tana ci gaba cikin sauri a cikin EU / EEA da Burtaniya.
Saboda haka, kasashe, asibitoci da raka'a masu kulawa da gaggawa ya kamata su shirya kansu don yanayin ci gaba da watsawar SARS-CoV-2 a cikin al'umma da kuma karuwar yawan marasa lafiya da ke fama da COVID-19 da ke buƙatar kula da lafiya, musamman ma kula da gaggawa, kamar wanda ke faruwa a yankunan da cutar ta shafa na Italiya.
Kamar yadda aka nuna a cikin binciken ECDC na kwanan nan, hanzari, mai aiki da kuma cikakkiyar hanya tana da mahimmanci don jinkirta yaduwar SARS-COV-2, tare da sauyawa daga hanyar hanawa zuwa hanyar ragewa, saboda tsammanin ƙaruwa mai sauri a cikin adadin shari'o'in na iya ba masu yanke shawara da asibitoci isasshen lokaci don fahimtar, karɓa da daidaita amsar su daidai idan ba a aiwatar da su ba a gaba.
A cikin saurin kimanta hadarin kuma an lissafa matakan kiwon lafiyar jama'a don rage tasirin cutar.
Akwai gajeren lokacin da ƙasashe za su iya ƙara haɓaka ƙoƙarin sarrafa su don rage yaduwar SARS-CoV-2 da rage matsin lamba akan kiwon lafiya.
Idan hakan bai faru ba, zai yiwu a samu karuwar marasa lafiya a cikin sauran kasashen EU/EEA da ke bukatar kulawa mai tsanani a cikin kwanaki ko makonni masu zuwa.
Cutar cutar Coronavirus 2019 (COVID-19), wanda cutar ta Coronavirus 2 (SARS-CoV-2), ta haifar da ta kashe mutane sama da 3,000 kuma ta kamu da fiye da 80,000 a China da sauran wurare a duniya, wanda ya haifar da bala'i ga mutane.
Kamar cutar ta homologous, SARS-CoV, wanda ya haifar da SARS a dubban mutane a 2003, SARS-CoV-2 na iya watsawa daga bats kuma yana haifar da irin waɗannan alamun ta hanyar irin wannan tsari.
Koyaya, COVID-19 yana da ƙarancin tsanani da mutuwa fiye da SARS amma yana da yawa fiye da watsawa kuma yana shafar tsofaffi fiye da matasa da maza fiye da mata.
