Saboda haka, COVID-19 na yanzu shine barkewar COVID-19 ta uku a tarihin ɗan adam.
Kamar yadda aka nuna a Fig. Fig.1,1, an fara bayar da rahoton tarin cututtukan huhu da ba a san asalin su ba daga Wuhan a ranar 31 ga Disamba, 2019 ga Hukumar Lafiya ta Kasa ta China.
Bayan kwana bakwai aka saki jerin abubuwan da suka faru.
A ranar 15 ga Janairu, 2020, an bayar da rahoton mutuwar farko daga Wuhan.
A lokacin, annobar ta bazu cikin sauri zuwa biranen da ke kusa da birnin, larduna, da kuma ƙasashe.
A ranar 20 ga Janairu, an ruwaito cewa an kamu da cutar a wurin masu kula da lafiya, wanda ya nuna cewa ana iya kamuwa da cutar daga mutum zuwa mutum.
A ranar 23 ga watan Janairu, an kulle birnin Wuhan tare da dakatar da duk hanyoyin sufuri na jama'a.
A ranar 24 ga Janairu binciken asibiti na farko kan cutar ya ba da rahoton cewa, daga cikin marasa lafiya 41 da aka tabbatar da cutar, 21 ne kawai suka yi hulɗa kai tsaye da kasuwar abincin teku ta Wuhan wanda aka ɗauka wuri ne na fara kamuwa da cutar daga asalin dabba da ba a sani ba.
A ranar 30 ga Janairu, WHO ta bayyana barkewar cutar a matsayin gaggawa ga lafiyar duniya.
A lokacin da aka gabatar da wannan rahoton, cutar ta riga ta yada a duk ƙasar Sin da kuma kusan wasu ƙasashe 50 a duniya (Fig. (Fig.2).2).
Yayin da yanayin ke ci gaba da sauri, har yanzu ana bukatar a ƙayyade yadda cutar za ta iya faɗa da kuma yadda za ta yi tsanani.
A ranar 11 ga Fabrairu, 2020, wani binciken cibiyoyin da yawa akan marasa lafiya 8,866 ciki har da marasa lafiya 4,021 da aka tabbatar da COVID-19 sun gabatar da ƙarin sabuntaccen kwatancin annobar kamar haka (https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/UlBi-HX_rHPXa1qHA2bhdA).
SARS-CoV-2 ya kamu da mutane na kowane zamani, amma galibi a cikin shekaru 30-65.
Kusan rabin (47.7%) na mutanen da suka kamu da cutar sun fi shekaru 50, kaɗan ne kawai suka kai shekara 20, kuma mutane 14 ne kawai suka kamu da cutar suka kai shekaru 10.
SARS-CoV-2 ya kamu da maza da yawa (0.31/100,000) fiye da mata (0.27/100,000).
COVID-19 ya faɗaɗa cikin rukuni galibi a cikin Hubei da kewaye da shi.
COVID-19 ya ɗauki matsakaici na kwanaki 5 (2-9) daga fara zuwa ganewar asali.
Matsakaicin lokacin incubacin ya kai kwanaki 4.8 (3.0-7.2).
