Baya ga abin rufe fuska, masu ba da sabis na kiwon lafiya ya kamata su sa rigunan keɓewa don rage haɗuwa da ƙwayoyin cuta.
Hakanan ƙwayoyin cuta na iya kamuwa da mutum ta idanunsu.
A ranar 22 ga Janairu, 2020, wani likita ya kamu da SARS-CoV-2 duk da cewa ya sa abin rufe fuska na N95; ƙila cutar ta shiga jikinsa ta idanunsa masu kumburi.
Saboda haka, masu kula da lafiya ya kamata su saka riguna masu tsabta ko tabarau yayin da suke aiki da marasa lafiya.
Ga jama'a a yankunan da cutar ta shafa ko kuma waɗanda za a iya shafawa, ana ba da shawarar sosai cewa kowa ya wanke hannayensu da sabulu mai kashe kashe cuta sau da yawa fiye da yadda aka saba, ya yi ƙoƙarin kasancewa a gida don keɓe kansa kuma ya rage hulɗa da mutanen da ke da cutar.
An yi la'akari da cewa kafa uku ne nesa da ya dace da mutane su guje wa wani mai haƙuri.
Wadannan ayyuka hanyoyi ne masu inganci don rage hadarin kamuwa da cuta da kuma hana yaduwar cutar.
Kodayake SARS-CoV-2 ya zo a matsayin sabon kwayar cutar ga duniyar ɗan adam, babban homologin sa ga SARS-CoV kamar yadda aka ruwaito a ranar 7 ga Janairu 2020 ya kamata ya haifar da babban faɗakarwa ga China bisa tushen ƙwaƙwalwar ta game da barkewar cutar SARS a 2003.
Duk da haka, ba har zuwa 19 ga Janairu 2020 ba ne darektan Cibiyar Kula da Cututtuka ta Wuhan ya ƙarfafa 'yan ƙasa ta hanyar cewa sabon kwayar cutar tana da ƙarancin kamuwa da cuta da iyakanceccen haifuwa daga mutum zuwa mutum kuma ba matsala ce don hana da kuma hana cutar.
Wannan sakon ya rage tsananin fargaba ga jama'a, musamman lokacin da duk kasar ke shirin bikin bazara, kuma an rasa lokacin da ya dace don hana cutar a ƙaramar sikelin da ta samu a Wuhan.
Hukumomin da ke kula da cututtuka a kasar Sin za su iya koyon darasi mai wuya kuma su yi gyara a nan gaba.
Alal misali, waɗannan hukumomi ya kamata su kasance (1) masu hankali yayin yin sanarwa a fili kamar yadda kowane kalma ke da mahimmanci ga 'yan ƙasa kuma zai iya canza halin su da yanke shawara; (2) mafi m da kuma amsawa ga bayanai na yau da kullun daga asibitoci maimakon jiran rahotanni na yau da kullun daga likitoci ko jami'ai; (3) mafi ƙuntatawa don hana yiwuwar annobar a farkon matakinta maimakon ƙoƙarin ta'azantar da jama'a; da kuma (4) mafi sau da yawa don ba da umarni na musamman da tasiri don ƙara wayar da kan jama'a game da cututtukan annobar da kuma gwadawa da inganta tsarin amsawar al'umma a lokaci-lokaci.
Fashewar COVID-19 da sabon kwayar cutar SARS-CoV-2 ta haifar ya fara ne a ƙarshen Disamba 2019.
A cikin kasa da watanni biyu, ya bazu ko'ina cikin China da kuma kusan wasu ƙasashe 50 a duniya a lokacin wannan rubuce-rubuce.
Tunda cutar ta yi kama da SARS-CoV kuma alamun sun yi kama da tsakanin COVID-19 da SARS, barkewar COVID-19 ta haifar da jin cewa SARS tana maimaitawa.
Duk da haka, akwai wasu bambance-bambance masu ban mamaki tsakanin COVID-19 da SARS, waɗanda ke da mahimmanci don hana annobar da kula da marasa lafiya.
COVID-19 yana shafar tsofaffi fiye da matasa da maza fiye da mata, kuma tsanani da yawan mutuwa suna da girma a cikin tsofaffi fiye da matasa.
SARS tana da mafi girma mutuwar fiye da COVID-19 (10.91% vs. 1.44%).
Marasa lafiya na COVID-19 suna watsa kwayar koda kuwa basu da alamun cutar yayin da marasa lafiya na SARS yawanci suke yin hakan lokacin da suke da mummunan rashin lafiya, wanda ke haifar da wahala sosai wajen hana yaduwar COVID-19 fiye da SARS.
Wannan ya bayyana a wani ɓangare dalilin da ya sa SARS-CoV-2 ya yadu da sauri kuma ya fi SARS-CoV yawa.
Gwajin RNA na yau da kullun don SARS-CoV-2 na iya zama mara kyau a cikin wasu marasa lafiya na COVID-19.
A wani bangare kuma, marasa lafiya da suka warke za su iya sake samun cutar.
Wadannan binciken sun kara hadarin yaduwar cutar sosai.
Ganin irin wannan ci gaban da ake samu cikin bincike kan COVID-19, har yanzu akwai wasu mahimman batutuwa da za a warware, kamar haka:
Daga ina SARS-CoV-2 ya fito?
Kodayake an gano homolog na kwayoyin halitta 96% tsakanin SARS-CoV-2 da CoVs biyu na SARS-kamar bats, har yanzu ba za mu iya kammala cewa SARS-CoV-2 daga bats ne ba.
Wane dabba ne ya ba da cutar daga wanda ya haife ta, wato, bats zuwa mutane?
Idan ba mu san amsoshin tambayoyi na 1 da 2 ba, ba za mu iya hana watsawa ba, kuma annobar za ta iya sake faruwa a kowane lokaci.
Kodayake samfurin kwayoyin halitta da nazarin halittu sun nuna cewa SARS-CoV-2 yana ɗaure da ACE2, ta yaya ainihin cutar ta shiga cikin ƙwayoyin hanyoyin numfashi kuma ta haifar da canje-canje na cutar?
Shin kwayar cutar tana ɗaure ƙwayoyin da ke nuna ACE2 a wasu gabobin jiki?
Idan ba mu sami amsoshi masu kyau ga waɗannan tambayoyin ba, ba za mu iya samun ganewar asali da kuma magani mai kyau ba.
Har yaushe cutar za ta ci gaba?
Ta yaya kwayar ta samo asali a lokacin da ake watsa ta tsakanin mutane?
Shin zai zama annoba a duniya, ya mutu kamar SARS ko kuma ya sake komawa a kai a kai kamar mura?
Yana da muhimmanci amma yana iya ɗaukar lokaci kafin a sami amsoshin waɗannan tambayoyin da kuma wasu tambayoyi da yawa.
Duk da haka, ko da yaya kudin da za mu kashe, ba mu da wani zaɓi sai dai mu dakatar da annobar da wuri-wuri kuma mu dawo da rayuwarmu zuwa al'ada.
Asalin zoonotic na kwayar cutar corona a cikin mutane
Cutar da kuma daidaitawa sun haifar da juyin halitta na kwayar cutar corona (CoVs) da masu karɓar bakinsu, gami da mutane, tsawon dubban shekaru.
Kafin 2003, an san cewa CoVs na mutum (HCoVs) biyu suna haifar da rashin lafiya mai sauƙi, kamar sanyi.
Fashewar cutar ta hanyar numfashi mai tsanani (SARS) da cutar ta hanyar numfashi ta Gabas ta Tsakiya (MERS) sun juya tsabar kudi don bayyana yadda cutar HCoV zata iya zama mai lalata da barazana ga rayuwa.
Fitowar SARS-CoV-2 a tsakiyar China a ƙarshen 2019 ta sake tura CoVs cikin hasken ido kuma ta ba mu mamaki da babban yaduwar sa amma rage cututtukan cututtuka idan aka kwatanta da 'yar'uwarta SARS-CoV.
kamuwa da cutar HCoV cutar dabba ce kuma fahimtar asalin HCoVs na dabba zai taimaka mana sosai.
Yawancin HCoVs sun samo asali ne daga bats inda ba su da cutar.
Hakanan an san masu karɓar ruwa na tsakiya na wasu HCoVs.
Gano dabbobi masu gida yana da tasiri kai tsaye a rigakafin cututtukan mutane.
Binciken hulɗar da CoV- mai masaukin baki a cikin dabbobi na iya samun muhimmiyar fahimta game da cutar CoV a cikin mutane.
A cikin wannan bita, muna gabatar da bayyani game da ilimin da ke akwai game da HCoVs bakwai, tare da mai da hankali kan tarihin gano su da kuma asalin su na zoonotic da watsa tsakanin jinsuna.
Yana da mahimmanci, muna kwatanta da bambanta HCoVs daga hangen nesa na juyin halitta na kwayar cutar da kuma sake haɗuwa da kwayoyin halitta.
Ana tattauna cutar COVID-19 ta yanzu a wannan mahallin.
Bugu da kari, an kuma nuna bukatun don sauyawar mai masaukin baki da kuma tasirin juyin halittar kwayar cutar akan cutar.
Coronaviruses (CoVs) suna cikin dangin Coronaviridae, wanda ya ƙunshi rukuni na ɓoye, mai kyau-ji, guda-tsiri RNA ƙwayoyin cuta.
Wadannan ƙwayoyin cuta waɗanda ke da babbar ƙwayoyin cuta na 26 zuwa 32 kilobases tsakanin ƙwayoyin cuta na RNA an kira su CoVs saboda yanayin su na kama da kambi a ƙarƙashin microscope na lantarki.
A tsarin, CoVs suna da kwayoyin halitta marasa rarrabuwa waɗanda ke da ƙungiya iri ɗaya.
Kimanin kashi biyu bisa uku na genom din sun ƙunshi manyan manyan manyan tsarin karatu (ORF1a da ORF1b), waɗanda aka fassara zuwa pp1a da pp1ab replicase polyproteins.
Ana sake sarrafa polyproteins don samar da sunadarai 16 wadanda ba na tsarin ba, wanda aka sanya nsp1 ~ 16.
Rashin ɓangaren kwayoyin halitta ya ƙunshi ORFs don furotin na tsarin, ciki har da spike (S), envelope (E), membrane (M) da nucleoprotein (N).
An kuma sanya wasu furotin na kayan aiki na musamman ta hanyar tsarin CoV daban-daban.
Dangane da bambancin jerin sunadarai, ana rarraba CoVs zuwa jinsuna huɗu (alpha-CoV, beta-CoV, gamma-CoV da delta-CoV), daga cikinsu jinsunan beta-CoV suna ƙunshe da yawancin HCoVs kuma an raba su zuwa zuriya huɗu (A, B, C da D).
Shaidar ilimin lissafi ta nuna cewa bats da rodents suna aiki a matsayin tushen gene na yawancin alpha-CoVs da beta-CoVs, yayin da tsuntsaye sune babban tanadin gamma-CoVs da delta-CoVs.
Shekaru dubbai, CoVs sun ci gaba da ƙetare shinge na jinsuna kuma wasu sun fito a matsayin manyan cututtukan mutum.
Ya zuwa yanzu, an san nau'ikan CoV bakwai na mutum (HCoVs).
Daga cikinsu HCoV-229E da HCoV-NL63 sune alpha-CoVs.
Sauran beta-CoVs guda biyar sun haɗa da HCoV-OC43, HCoV-HKU1, mawuyacin cututtukan numfashi na cutar coronavirus (SARS-CoV), cutar coronavirus ta ciwon huhu ta Gabas ta Tsakiya (MERS-CoV) da SARS-CoV-2.
HCoV-229E, HCoV-OC43, HCoV-HKU1 da HCoV-NL63 yawanci suna haifar da alamun bayyanar cututtuka, kamar sanyi na yau da kullun da / ko fitsari.
Sabanin haka, SARS-CoV, MERS-CoV da sabon gano SARS-CoV-2 suna da cutar cututtuka sosai, suna haifar da kamuwa da cututtukan ƙananan hanyoyin numfashi a cikin marasa lafiya da yawa tare da mafi girman damar haɓaka cututtukan cututtukan numfashi mai tsanani (ARDS) da bayyanar cututtukan huhu.
An ware nau'in HCoV-229E na farko, B814, daga zubar da hanci na marasa lafiya da mura a tsakiyar shekarun 1960.
Tun daga wannan lokacin, an tara ƙarin ilimi ta hanyar nazarin zurfi akan HCoV-229E da HCoV-OC43, duka biyun suna haifar da alamun da ke iyakance kansu.
A zahiri, an yarda da ra'ayin cewa kamuwa da cutar HCoVs gabaɗaya ba ta da lahani har sai barkewar SARS.
Cutar SARS da ta faru a shekara ta 2003 ita ce mafi muni a tarihin zamani, ta kamu da mutane sama da 8,000 tare da mutuwar kashi 10% na cutar.
Shekaru goma bayan haka, annobar cutar ta hanyar numfashi ta Gabas ta Tsakiya (MERS) ta jawo ci gaba da yaduwar cutar a yankin Larabawa kuma ta bazu zuwa sauran duniya.
Sabuwar cutar HCoV ta 2019 (2019-nCoV), wanda daga baya aka sake masa suna SARS-CoV-2, ita ce mai haifar da annobar cutar coronavirus ta 2019 (COVID-19), wanda ya kashe fiye da 3,120 kuma ya kamu da mutane sama da 91,000 a ranar 3 ga Maris, 2020.
An yi ta yin gargadi kuma dole ne duniya ta shirya don annobar SARS-CoV-2 mai zuwa.
Dukkanin HCoVs bakwai suna da asalin zoonotic daga bats, beraye ko dabbobi na gida.
Lines da yawa na shaida suna tallafawa asalin juyin halitta na duk HCoVs daga bats, inda ƙwayoyin cuta suka dace da kyau kuma ba su da cutar amma suna nuna bambancin kwayoyin halitta mai yawa.
Cutar COVID-19 ta kawo gagarumin kalubale na kiwon lafiya, kimiyya, zamantakewa da kuma halin kirki ga Sin da duniya.
Bin diddigin asalin HCoVs na zoonotic yana ba da tsarin fahimtar tarihin halitta, ƙarfin motsawa da abubuwan ƙuntatawa na tsalle-tsalle na jinsuna.
Wannan kuma na iya jagorantar ko sauƙaƙe binciken tanadi, matsakaici da haɓaka dabbobi masu karɓar bakuncin SARS-CoV-2, tare da mahimman tasirin rigakafin ɓarkewar gaba.
A cikin wannan bita mun gabatar da bayyani game da asalin zoonotic, watsa tsakanin jinsuna da kuma kamuwa da cutar HCoVs.
Musamman, muna nunawa da tattauna batun gama gari cewa ƙwayoyin cuta na HCoVs na iyaye galibi ba su da cutar a cikin masu karɓar bakuncin su na halitta amma sun zama masu cutar bayan watsa tsakanin nau'ikan zuwa sabon mai karɓar.
Mun kuma sake nazarin yanayin juyin halittar HCoV inda karuwar kamuwa da cutar sau da yawa yakan zo tare da raguwar cutar.
An kuma tattauna sakamakon barkewar cutar SARS-CoV-2 a wannan mahallin.
An san dabbobi tun daga ƙarshen shekarun 1930.
Kafin warewar farko ta HCoV-229E strain B814 daga fitowar hanci na marasa lafiya waɗanda suka kamu da sanyi na yau da kullun, an ware nau'ikan CoVs daban-daban a cikin dabbobi daban-daban da suka kamu da cutar, gami da turkey, linzamin kwamfuta, saniya, alade, cat da kare.
A cikin shekarun da suka gabata, an gano HCoVs bakwai.
Takaitaccen taƙaitaccen tarihin gano HCoV a cikin tsari na lokaci (Table 1) zai zama mai ba da bayani da kuma koyawa.
An ware nau'in HCoV-229E na farko daga hanyoyin numfashi na marasa lafiya da ke da kamuwa da cutar ta hanyar numfashi a shekara ta 1966, kuma daga baya an daidaita shi don girma a cikin layukan ƙwayoyin huhu na WI-38.
Marasa lafiya da ke kamuwa da cutar HCoV-229E sun nuna alamun sanyi na yau da kullun, gami da ciwon kai, cizon yatsa, rashin lafiya da ciwon wuya, tare da zazzabi da tari da aka gani a cikin 10 ~ 20% na lokuta.
Daga baya a 1967, an ware HCoV-OC43 daga al'adun kwayoyin halitta da kuma wucewa ta hanyar layi a cikin kwakwalwar beraye masu shayarwa.
Abubuwan asibiti na kamuwa da cutar HCoV-OC43 suna kama da waɗanda HCoV-229E ya haifar, wanda ba a iya bambanta su da bayyanar cututtuka tare da sauran cututtukan hanyoyin numfashi kamar ƙwayoyin cuta na A da rhinoviruses.
Dukansu HCoV-229E da HCoV-OC43 suna rarraba a duniya, kuma suna da saurin watsawa a lokacin hunturu a cikin yanayin zafi.
Yawanci, lokacin shan waɗannan ƙwayoyin cuta guda biyu bai kai mako ɗaya ba, kuma a bi shi da kusan mako biyu na rashin lafiya.
A cewar wani binciken da aka yi na masu sa kai a kan mutane, mutane masu lafiya da suka kamu da cutar HCoV-229E sun kamu da sanyi mai sauƙi.
Wasu marasa lafiya da ke fama da rashin lafiyan jiki ne kawai suka kamu da cututtukan ƙananan hanyoyin numfashi.
SARS, wanda aka fi sani da atypical pneumonia, shine cutar ta farko da aka rubuta da kyau ta hanyar HCoV a tarihin ɗan adam kuma wakili na etiological shine SARS-CoV, HCoV na uku da aka gano.
Ana iya gano farkon cutar SARS a ƙarshen 2002 a lardin Guangdong na kasar Sin.
Cutar SARS ta haifar da shari'o'i 8,096 da aka ruwaito tare da mutuwar 774, wanda ya bazu a cikin ƙasashe da nahiyoyi da yawa.
Baya ga masu yadawa, an kiyasta cewa kowane hali zai iya haifar da kimanin shari'o'i biyu na biyu, tare da lokacin incuba na kwanaki 4 zuwa 7 kuma ƙwanƙolin ƙwayar cuta yana bayyana a ranar 10 ta rashin lafiya.
Marasa lafiya da suka kamu da SARS-CoV da farko suna da myalgia, ciwon kai, zazzabi, rashin lafiya da sanyi, sannan dyspnea, tari da wahalar numfashi a matsayin alamun bayyanar cututtuka.
Lymphopenia, gwajin aikin hanta da kuma karuwar creatine kinase sune cututtukan dakin gwaje-gwaje na SARS.
An kuma lura da lalacewar alveolar da ta bazu, yaduwar kwayoyin epithelial da karuwar macrophages a cikin marasa lafiya na SARS.
Kimanin kashi 20-30 na marasa lafiya suna bukatar kulawa mai tsanani da kuma iska mai iska.
Baya ga ƙananan hanyoyin numfashi, gabobin jiki da yawa ciki har da na gastrointestinal tract, hanta da koda na iya kamuwa da cutar a cikin waɗannan mawuyacin hali, yawanci tare da hadari na cytokine, wanda zai iya zama mai kisa musamman a cikin marasa lafiya da ke da rashin lafiya.
An fara ware cutar ne daga binciken da aka yi a huhu na wani dangi na mai cutar da ya zo Hong Kong daga Guangzhou.
Tun daga lokacin, an yi ƙoƙari sosai wajen gudanar da bincike kan cutar HCoV.
An ware HCoV-NL63 daga wani yaro mai watanni 7 daga Netherlands a ƙarshen 2004.
Da farko an gano cewa yana da yawa a cikin yara ƙanana, tsofaffi da marasa lafiya da ke fama da cututtukan numfashi.
Bayyana coryza, conjunctivitis, zazzabi, da bronchiolitis na kowa ne a cikin cutar da HCoV-NL63 ta haifar.
Wani bincike mai zaman kansa ya bayyana warewar wannan kwayar daga samfurin hanci daga wani yaro mai watanni 8 da ke fama da cutar huhu a Netherlands.
Ko da yake an gano shi a Netherlands, a zahiri an rarraba shi a duniya.
An kiyasta cewa HCoV-NL63 yana da kusan kashi 4.7% na cututtukan numfashi na yau da kullun, kuma mafi yawan cututtukan yana faruwa a farkon bazara, bazara da hunturu.
HCoV-NL63 yana da alaƙa da cututtukan laryngitis na hanawa, wanda aka fi sani da croup.
A wannan shekarar, an ware HCoV-HKU1 daga wani mutum mai shekaru 71 wanda aka kwantar da shi asibiti tare da ciwon huhu da bronchiolitis a Hong Kong.
Baya ga cutar huhu da bronchiolitis da aka samu a cikin al'umma, an ruwaito HCoV-HKU1 yana da alaƙa da matsanancin ɓacin asma.
Kamar HCoV-NL63, HCoV-229E da HCoV-OC43, an gano HCoV-HKU1 a duk duniya, yana haifar da cututtukan numfashi masu sauƙi.
Dukkanin wadannan HCoVs huɗu da aka samu a cikin al'umma sun dace da mutane sosai kuma gabaɗaya ba sa da yiwuwar canzawa don haifar da cututtukan cututtuka masu cutar, kodayake haɗari sun faru saboda dalilai da ba a sani ba kamar a cikin wani hali mai wuya na nau'in HCoV-NL63, wanda kwanan nan aka ruwaito yana haifar da kamuwa da cutar ta hanyar numfashi a cikin China.
Gabaɗaya, lokacin da waɗannan HCoVs suka sami ikon watsawa yadda ya kamata kuma su ci gaba da kasancewa cikin mutane, suna zama marasa ƙarfi ko masu cutar.
An fara ware MERS-CoV a shekarar 2012 daga huhu na wani mai shekaru 60 da haihuwa wanda ya kamu da cutar huhu mai tsanani da kuma rashin aikin koda a Saudiyya.
Yayin da yawancin lokuta da aka tabbatar da su a dakin gwaje-gwaje suka fito ne daga Gabas ta Tsakiya, an ruwaito wasu lokuta da aka shigo da su daga ƙasashen Turai da Tunisia da kuma wasu ƙasashen da aka yi amfani da su wajen yin hulɗa da su.
Wani annobar na biyu ya faru a Koriya ta Kudu a shekarar 2015 tare da kamuwa da cutar 186 da aka tabbatar.
Halin da ake nunawa a asibiti na MERS ya yi kama da na SARS, wanda ake nuna shi ta hanyar ci gaba da kamuwa da cutar huhu.
Ba kamar SARS ba, yawancin marasa lafiya da ke da MERS sun sami rashin aikin koda mai tsanani, wanda har yanzu ya zama na musamman ga MERS tsakanin cututtukan da HCoV ke haifarwa.
Fiye da kashi 30% na marasa lafiya suna da alamun cututtukan gastrointestinal, kamar fitsari da amai.
Ya zuwa 14 ga Fabrairu, 2020, an ba da rahoton fiye da shari'o'in da aka tabbatar da su a cikin dakin gwaje-gwaje sama da 2500 tare da yawan mutuwar mutane da suka kai kashi 34.4%, wanda ya sa MERS-CoV ya zama ɗayan ƙwayoyin cuta mafi lalacewa da aka sani ga mutane.
A tsakiyar zuwa ƙarshen Disamba 2019, an gano tarin marasa lafiya na cutar huhu da aka sani a baya cewa suna da alaƙa da kamuwa da cutar SARS-CoV-2 a Wuhan, lardin Hubei, China.
Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya ta ayyana barkewar kamuwa da cutar ta hanyar numfashi ta kasa da ta haifar da SARS-CoV-2 a matsayin gaggawa na Lafiya ta Jama'a na Kula da Lafiya ta Duniya kuma ta sanya sunan cutar COVID-19.
Ya zuwa 3 ga Maris, 2020, an tabbatar da shari'o'i 90,053 a duk duniya, tare da mutuwar kashi 3.4%.
A cikin wannan yanayin, yawan mutuwar mutane a Hubei, China, ya kai 4.2%, yayin da a waje da shi ya kai 1.2%.
SARS-CoV-2 yana haifar da kamuwa da cutar numfashi mai tsanani kamar SARS-CoV da MERS-CoV, wanda aka gabatar a matsayin zazzabi, tari da rashin numfashi.
Ana kuma ganin ciwon ciki a wasu marasa lafiya.
Ciwon huhu yana ɗaya daga cikin alamun da suka fi tsanani kuma yana iya saurin zama ciwon huhu mai tsanani.
Kodayake SARS-CoV da SARS-CoV-2 suna da kamanceceniya sosai saboda homology na jerin nucleotide mai girma na 82%, suna haɗuwa cikin rassa daban-daban a cikin itacen phylogenetic.
SARS-CoV-2 a bayyane yake ba shi da ƙwayoyin cuta amma yana da sauƙin watsawa idan aka kwatanta da SARS-CoV da MERS-CoV.
An bayar da rahoton mutane marasa alamun cutar da suka kamu da cutar SARS-CoV-2 kuma suna iya taimakawa wajen saurin yaduwar ta a duniya.
Kwatanta da bambanta SARS-CoV-2 da sauran HCoVs shida ya nuna kamanceceniya da bambance-bambance masu ban sha'awa.
