Baya ga abubuwa uku na kwayar cuta da aka ambata a sama, hulɗar kwayar cuta da mai karɓar mai karɓar wani muhimmin abu ne mai tasiri a watsa tsakanin jinsuna.
A nan, ana ɗaukar sake haɗuwa da SARS-CoV a matsayin misali na yau da kullun, wanda kuma ya nuna hujjojin zaɓi mai kyau yayin abubuwan watsa tsakanin nau'ikan.
Dangane da kwatancen bincike tsakanin ɓangarorin SARS-CoVs na ɗan adam da na ɗan adam, ana tsammanin SARS-CoV ya sami saurin daidaitawa a cikin masu masaukin baki daban-daban, musamman tare da canji a RBD na furotin S.
Gabaɗaya, RBD a cikin furotin S na CoV yana hulɗa da mai karɓar sel kuma ana zaɓar shi sosai ta hanyar amsawar rigakafin mai masaukin baki.
A cikin SARS-CoV, RBD yana cikin amino acid na 318 zuwa 510 akan ɓangaren S1, wanda ke ɗaure da ACE2 na ɗan adam da kuma coreceptors don shigar da kwayar cutar.
RBD na SARS-CoV yana iya gane masu karɓar ACE2 na dabbobi daban-daban, gami da bats, civet, linzamin kwamfuta da kare raccoon, yana ba da damar watsa kwayar cutar tsakanin jinsuna.
A gaskiya ma, an lura da amino acid 6 kawai da suka bambanta da kwayoyin cuta na mutum da na civet a cikin RBD kuma 4 daga cikinsu suna cikin ƙwayar mai ɗaurewa don hulɗa da mai karɓar ACE2.
Civet SARS-CoV yana da K479N da S487T mutations a cikin RBD, wanda zai iya haɓaka haɗuwa da hulɗar furotin mai ƙwanƙwasa tare da mai karɓar ACE2 na ɗan adam.
A wasu kalmomi, waɗannan maye gurbin amino acid biyu na iya zama masu muhimmanci ga daidaitawar kwayar cutar ga mutane.
Yana da mahimmanci cewa SARS-CoV-2 yana da karɓar sel iri ɗaya tare da SARS-CoV.
Bambanci na 30% tsakanin SARS-CoV-2 da SARS-CoV a cikin sashin S1 na furotin S yana nuna cewa alaƙar haɗin furotin S da ACE2 na ɗan adam na iya canzawa.
A zahiri, binciken cryo-EM ya nuna cewa wannan haɗin yana da alaƙa sau 10 zuwa 20 fiye da na tsakanin ƙwayoyin ACE2 na mutum da SARS-CoV S.
Hakanan zai zama da ban sha'awa don tantance ko ana buƙatar wani coreceptor don watsa SARS-CoV-2.
Abin sha'awa, HCoV-NL63 kuma yana ɗaure da ACE2 amma tare da wani ɓangare na S.
Akwai sauran masu karɓar HCoV da yawa, kamar aminopeptidase N don HCoV-229E, da 9-O-acetylated sialic acid don HCoV-OC43.
Hakanan zasu iya ba da lissafin nasarar daidaita waɗannan CoVs a cikin mutane bayan watsa tsakanin jinsuna daga dabbobi masu masaukin su.
Baya ga masu karɓar sel, sakamakon watsa HCoVs tsakanin nau'ikan kuma yana ƙarƙashin sauran abubuwan dogaro da ƙuntatawa na mai masaukin baki.
Bambanci na waɗannan furotin masu karɓar baƙi tsakanin mutane da masu karɓar HCoVs na halitta kamar bats, rakumi dromedary da rodents na iya zama shinge ga watsa tsakanin jinsuna.
HCoVs dole ne su karɓi abubuwan dogaro da mai masaukin baki da kuma lalata abubuwan hana masaukin baki don nasarar watsa tsakanin jinsuna.
A wannan yanayin, ana iya ganowa da kuma nuna halaye masu ƙayyadewa na kwayoyin a wannan muhimmin yanki na hulɗa da kwayar cuta.
Yin bincike ba tare da nuna bambanci ba a cikin dukkanin kwayoyin halittar mutum game da masu karɓar baƙi da abubuwan hanawa SARS-CoV-2 ta amfani da fasahar zamani ta CRISPR na iya zama mai amfani.
Fitowar sabbin HCoVs: koma zuwa ƙasa sifili
Bambancin CoVs na bats yana ba da dama mai yawa don fitowar sabbin HCoVs.
A wannan ma'anar, CoVs na bats suna aiki ne a matsayin tarin kwayoyin HCoVs.
Bugu da kari, saurin maye gurbin da kuma sake haɗuwa da kwayoyin halittar halittar halittar HCoV kuma suna aiki a matsayin matakai biyu masu mahimmanci a cikin wannan tsari.
Alal misali, saye ko asarar sababbin kwayoyin gina jiki masu ƙididdigar sunadaran suna da damar canza tsarin ƙwayar cuta.
Daga cikin furotin na SARS-CoV, an yi tunanin ORF8 yana da mahimmanci wajen daidaitawa ga mutane, kamar yadda aka ware kwayar cutar bat da ke da alaƙa da SARS-CoV amma an gano cewa tana ba da furotin ORF8 daban-daban.
An gano fasalin kawar da nucleotide 29 na SARS-CoVs a cikin nau'ikan da aka keɓe a farkon annobar ɗan adam.
Wannan sharewa ya raba ORF8 zuwa ORF8a da ORF8b kuma ana tsammanin shi ne maye gurbin da ke inganta sauyawar masu masauki.
Bugu da ƙari, SARS-CoV yana da tarihin sake haɗuwa da zuriyar alpha- da gamma-CoVs, inda aka gano ƙananan ƙananan yankuna masu haɗuwa a cikin RNA-daidaitaccen RNA polymerase.
An kuma gano wuraren sake haɗuwa a cikin nsp9, mafi yawan nsp10, da kuma sassa na nsp14.
Hakazalika, an nuna cewa annobar MERS-CoV ta sami abubuwan sake haɗuwa tsakanin zuriyoyi daban-daban, wanda ya faru a cikin raƙuman dromedary a Saudi Arabia.
Baya ga SARS-CoV da MERS-CoV, an lura da abubuwan sake haɗuwa a cikin sauran HCoVs, inda HCoVs suka sake haɗuwa da sauran CoVs na dabba a cikin kwayoyin su na ba-tsara.
Ya kamata kuma a yi gargadi cewa zabin mutum na iya taimakawa wajen sauye-sauye da ba a so a cikin kwayoyin halitta na kwayar cuta, wanda ya fi dacewa ya haifar da kawar da ƙwayoyin cuta daga matsin zabin da aka yi, kamar na tsarin rigakafi na mai masaukin baki.
Misali na waɗannan tasirin shine asarar cikakken tsawon ORF4 a cikin nau'in samfurin HCoV-229E, saboda kawar da nucleotide biyu.
Duk da yake ana iya lura da ORF4 mai kyau a cikin kwayar cutar bats da raƙuma da ke da alaƙa da HCoV-229E, alpaca alpha-CoV yana nuna shigar nucleotide guda ɗaya, wanda ya haifar da canjin tsarin.
A ƙarshe amma ba mafi ƙarancin ba, juyin halittar sabon HCoVs kuma yana motsawa ne ta hanyar matsin zaɓa a cikin masu karɓar bakuncin su.
An gano alamun bayyanar cututtuka marasa alama ko kuma masu sauƙi ne kawai lokacin da bats suka kamu da CoVs, wanda ke nuna daidaitawar juna tsakanin CoVs da bats.
An bayyana cewa bats suna da kyau da aka daidaita zuwa CoVs anatomically da physiologically.
Alal misali, lahani a cikin kunna amsa mai ƙonewa a cikin bats yana rage cututtukan da CoVs ke jawowa.
Bugu da ƙari, aikin ƙwayoyin halitta masu kisa a cikin bats an danne shi saboda haɓakar ƙwayar ƙwayar halitta mai kisa mai hanawa NKG2/CD94 da ƙananan matakin bayyanawa na manyan kwayoyin haɗin haɗin gwiwa na aji na I.
Bugu da ƙari, babban matakin nau'ikan oxygen mai aiki (ROS) da aka samar daga babban aikin maye gurbin bats zai iya hana kwafin CoV kuma ya shafi gyarawa ta exoribonuclease, don haka samar da matsin lamba don samar da nau'ikan kwayar cutar da ke da cutar sosai lokacin da aka gabatar da su a cikin sabon mai masaukin baki.
Ƙarin kwayoyin CoV na iya samo asali ta hanyar sake haɗuwa, wanda ke haifar da samun sababbin furotin ko siffofin furotin don daidaitawar mai masaukin baki.
Saboda haka, ba zato ba tsammani bane cewa sabbin HCoVs guda uku sun bayyana a cikin shekaru ashirin da suka gabata.
CoVs ba su da cututtuka ko kuma suna haifar da alamun bayyanar cututtuka a cikin masu karɓar bakinsu kamar bats da raƙuma.
Suna yin kwayar halitta sosai ba tare da su jawo rigakafin jiki ba.
A nan ne asirin dalilin da ya sa ake ganin masu dauke da cututtuka marasa alamar cututtuka da kuma abin da ke haddasa cututtuka masu tsanani a cikin mutum.
Alamun cututtuka sun fi yawa saboda yawan aikin rigakafi da kuma hadarin cytokine inda idan amsawar rigakafi ta kasance mai karfi, cutar huhu za ta fi tsanani.
Akasin haka, a cikin masu dauke da cututtuka marasa alamar cututtuka, an cire maganin rigakafi daga kwayar cutar CoV.
Hanyar da ta dace ta kawar da maganin rigakafi na iya samun sakamako mai kyau a maganin cutar SARS-CoV-2.
Amsar interferon tana da ƙarfi sosai a cikin bats.
Saboda haka, gudanar da interferon nau'in I aƙalla a farkon matakin kamuwa da cutar SARS-CoV-2 a cikin mutane ya kamata ya kasance mai amfani.
Bugu da ƙari, NLRP3 yana da lahani a cikin bats.
Ta wannan hanyar, hana NLRP3 kumburi tare da MCC950 na iya zama da amfani a cikin maganin COVID-19.
Fitowar SARS-CoV-2 ya biyo bayan jigon da SARS-CoV da MERS-CoV suka samo asali.
Yayin da aka gano wani bat beta-CoV wanda ke da kashi 95% na homology na nucleotide tare da SARS-CoV, akwai kuma wani bat-CoV wanda ke da kashi 96% na homology na nucleotide tare da SARS-CoV-2.
Yayin da aka gano cewa civets da sauran dabbobi a kasuwannin suna da ƙwayoyin cuta iri ɗaya da SARS-CoV, ba a gano masu karɓar bakuncin SARS-CoV-2 ba.
An gano pangolin beta-CoVs masu kama da SARS-CoV-2, wanda ke nuna cewa pangolin na iya zama ɗayan masu karɓar bakuncin matsakaici ko pangolin beta-CoVs na iya ba da gudummawar ɓangarorin gene ga sigar ƙarshe ta SARS-CoV-2.
Ko da yake tambayoyi sun kasance, babu wata hujja cewa SARS-CoV-2 an yi ta ne da gangan ko kuma ba zato ba tsammani.
CoVs sun koma cikin hasken rana saboda barkewar cutar SARS-CoV-2.
Nazarin CoVs a cikin bats da sauran dabbobi ya canza tunaninmu sosai game da mahimmancin asalin zoonotic da wuraren adana dabbobi na HCoVs a cikin watsawar ɗan adam.
Shaidu masu yawa sun nuna cewa SARS-CoV, MERS-CoV da SARS-CoV-2 suna da asalin yatsa kuma ana watsa su ga mutane ta hanyar masu karɓar bakuncin matsakaici.
Ganin cewa kamuwa da cutar SARS-CoV ta samo asali ne daga hulɗa tsakanin mutane da fararen fata a kasuwanni, rufe kasuwanni masu ruwa da kashe fararen fata a ciki na iya kawo ƙarshen annobar SARS.
Ta wannan dalili, ya kamata a cire pangolin daga kasuwannin rigar don hana yaduwar zoonotic, saboda gano zuriya da yawa na pangolin beta-CoVs da ke da alaƙa da SARS-CoV-2.
Koyaya, ko kuma yadda SARS-CoV-2 ke watsawa ga mutane ta hanyar pangolins da sauran dabbobi masu shayarwa har yanzu ana bayyana su a cikin binciken da za a yi a nan gaba.
A gefe guda, MERS-CoV ya kasance a cikin raƙuman dromedary na dogon lokaci.
Waɗannan raƙuman suna da muhimmanci wajen sufuri da kuma tushen nama, madara, fata da kayayyakin ulu ga mutanen yankin.
An rarraba su sosai a Gabas ta Tsakiya da Afirka.
Saboda haka ba zai yiwu a sadaukar da dukkan raƙuma don sarrafa MERS ba, kamar yadda aka yi a kasuwannin dabbobin daji a China don hana yaduwar SARS-CoV da SARS-CoV-2.
Don dakatar da sake barkewar cutar MERS, ya kamata a dauki cikakken tsari don samar da ingantattun alluran rigakafi na MERS-CoV ga raƙuma, a hade da sauran matakan hana kamuwa da cuta.
Tun da ba za mu iya kawar da waɗannan ƙwayoyin ba, za a iya samun sababbin nau'o'in kwayoyin halitta da za su iya haifar da barkewar cutar.
Akwai nau'i-nau'i na CoVs da ke yawo a cikin daji.
Musamman, CoVs na bats da ke da damar zoonotic suna da bambanci sosai.
Akwai dama mai yawa da wadannan CoVs na zoonotic za su samu ci gaba da kuma sake haɗuwa, wanda zai haifar da fitowar sababbin CoVs da za su iya kamuwa da su kuma/ko su zama masu kisa ga mutane a nan gaba.
Ya kamata a daina cin dabbobi a wasu wurare a kasar Sin don rage hulɗa da dabbobi da mutane.
Tare da wahalar SARS, MERS da COVID-19, ya kamata a kafa shiri da shirin amsawa mafi kyau.
A gaskiya, ƙwayoyin cuta da yawa sun daɗe suna wanzuwa a duniya.
Suna zama a cikin wuraren da suke ajiye ruwa har sai an samu damar yin hakan.
Ko da yake bats suna da halaye da yawa da ke taimaka wa mutane su yi yaduwar ƙwayoyin cuta, za a iya rage haɗarin da mutane suke da shi da bats da sauran jinsunan dabbobin daji idan aka koya wa mutane su guji su.
Ana bukatar ci gaba da lura da dabbobi masu shayarwa domin a fahimci yanayin halittu na CoVs da kuma wadanda suke da su a yanayi, wanda zai zama da amfani wajen hana yaduwar dabba zuwa mutum da kuma barkewar cutar a nan gaba.
A ƙarshe, hanya mafi inganci don hana cutar zoonosis ita ce mutane su nisanta kansu daga yanayin halittu na wuraren ajiyar kwayoyin halitta na ƙwayoyin cuta.
Har yanzu akwai wasu abubuwa da suka ɓace a cikin jigon asalin SARS-CoV-2.
Da farko, idan bats suka watsa kwayar cutar SARS-CoV-2 ga pangolins, zai zama da ban sha'awa a ga a wace yanayi bats da pangolins zasu iya raba yanayin muhalli iri ɗaya.
Na biyu, idan bats suna da matsayi na musamman wajen watsawa, ya kamata a san yadda mutane suke tuntuɓar bats.
Na uku, idan dabba mai shayarwa ta uku ta zama mai masaukin baki na gaskiya, dole ne a bayyana yadda take hulɗa da jinsuna daban-daban ciki har da mutane, bats da pangolins.
A ƙarshe, tun da dabbobi masu shayarwa da yawa ciki har da dabbobin gida na iya zama masu saurin kamuwa da SARS-CoV-2, ya kamata a gudanar da saka idanu da kuma kamuwa da cutar gwaji.
Idan ya kasance yatsa, pangolin ko wani dabba mai shayarwa, ana sa ran cewa za a gano SARS-CoV-2 ko kwayoyin iyayensa waɗanda kusan iri ɗaya ne a cikin mahaifarsa na halitta a nan gaba.
Ci gaba da bincike a wannan fannin zai bayyana hanyar juyin halitta na SARS-CoV-2 a cikin dabbobi, tare da mahimman tasirin rigakafi da sarrafa COVID-19 a cikin mutane.
Ana bukatar sabunta ka'idodin ganewar asali na COVID-19 mutumin da ake zargi  da kuma mutumin da aka tabbatar 
A ranar 6 ga Fabrairu, 2020, ƙungiyarmu ta buga jagorar shawara mai sauri don ganewa da magani na cutar coronavirus (2019-nCoV) ta shekara ta 2019, kuma wannan jagorar ta ba da kwarewarmu kuma tana da kyakkyawar ma'ana don yaƙar wannan annobar a duk duniya.
Koyaya, cutar coronavirus 2019 (COVID-19) sabuwar cuta ce, hankali da iliminmu suna ƙaruwa a hankali bisa ga binciken bincike da ƙwarewar aikin asibiti; saboda haka, ana sabunta dabarun bincike da magani koyaushe.
A cikin wannan wasikar, mun amsa wani bayani game da jagorarmu kuma mun samar da sabbin ka'idodin ganewar asali na masu zargin hali da masu tabbatar da hali bisa ga sabuwar Jagorar Ganowa da Kulawa don COVID-19 (sarrafa ta bakwai) da Kwamitin Lafiya na Jamhuriyar Jama'ar Sin ya fitar.
A watan Disamba na 2019, sabon coronavirus na 2019 (2019-nCoV) ya haifar da barkewar cutar, wanda yanzu ana kiran shi da sunan cutar coronavirus 2019 (COVID-19) kuma an sanya sunan cutar ta coronavirus 2 (SARS-CoV-2).
A ranar 11 ga Maris, 2020, WHO ta bayyana COVID-19 a matsayin annoba.
Don yaƙi da kamuwa da cutar SARS-CoV-2, ƙungiyarmu ta haɓaka jagorar shawara mai sauri kuma an buga ta ta kan layi a cikin Nazarin Likitan Soja a ranar 06 ga Fabrairu 2020.
Tun lokacin da aka buga shi, mutane sun mai da hankali sosai.
Ka lura duk da haka cewa COVID-19 sabon cuta ne, hankali da iliminmu suna ƙaruwa a hankali bisa ga binciken bincike da kuma kwarewar aikin asibiti; saboda haka, ana sabunta dabarun bincike da magani koyaushe.
Misali, Jagorar Bincike da Kula da COVID-19 da Kwamitin Lafiya na Kasa na Jamhuriyar Jama'ar Sin (http://www.nhc.gov.cn/) ya fitar, tsakanin 16 ga Janairu 2020 zuwa 3 ga Maris 2020, ya fitar da bugu bakwai tare da wasu mahallin da aka canza sosai.
Yanzu jagorarmu ta karbi tsokaci daga Zhou da sauransu, sun gabatar da wata shawara mai sauki dangane da kwarewarsu ta asibiti.
Aikin su ya kara da cewa akwai sabbin hujjoji ga jagorarmu kuma yana da mahimmanci ga wannan annobar a duniya.
Muna goyon bayan aikin da suke yi kuma muna gode musu.
Duk da haka, aikin su kuma yana buƙatar sabuntawa bisa ga sabon Maganar Gano da Kulawa don COVID-19 (Fita na bakwai) da kuma binciken kwanan nan.
A cewar bugu na bakwai (3 ga Maris 2020), don tabbatar da zargin cutar ya kamata a haɗa kowane abu na tarihin cututtukan cututtuka tare da abubuwa biyu na bayyanar cututtuka don yin cikakken bincike, ko kuma ya kamata a sadu da abubuwa uku na bayyanar cututtuka idan ba tare da bayyanar cututtuka ba:
Tarihin cututtukan cututtuka: (1) tarihin tafiya ko zama a birnin Wuhan da yankunan da ke kewaye da shi, ko wasu al'ummomin da aka ruwaito shari'o'in COVID-19 a cikin kwanaki 14 na ƙarshe kafin farawar bayyanar cututtuka; (2) tarihin tuntuɓar cututtuka masu kamuwa da cutar SARS-CoV-2 (tare da gwajin nucleic acid mai kyau); (3) tarihin tuntuɓar marasa lafiya da ke da zazzabi ko alamun numfashi daga birnin Wuhan da yankunan da kewaye da shi, ko wasu al'ummomin da aka ruwaito COVID-19 a cikin kwanaki 14 na ƙarshe kafin farawar bayyanar cututtuka; (4) tarihin tuntuɓar rukuni na tabbataccen shari'o'in (≥ 2 lokuta da ke da zazzabi da / ko alamun numfashi sun faru a cikin makonni 2 a cikin ƙananan yankuna, kamar gida, ofis, aji na makaranta, da sauransu).
Bayyanar asibiti: (1) zazzabi da / ko alamun numfashi; (2) tare da siffofin daukar hoto na kamuwa da COVID-19; (3) jimlar ƙididdigar ƙwayoyin fari na jini da ke nuna al'ada, raguwa, ko raguwar ƙididdigar lymphocyte a farkon matakin farawa.
Ana buƙatar tantance tabbataccen yanayin bisa ga wata sanannen sanannen sanarwa da wata alama ta cutar ko kuma na binciken kwayoyin halitta kamar haka: (1) gwajin PCR na ainihi mai kyau ga SARS-CoV-2; (2) jerin kwayoyin cuta na ƙwayar cuta mai ƙwayar cuta wanda ke nuna babban daidaituwa da sanannun ƙwayoyin cuta na coronavirus; (3) tabbatacce ga takamaiman IgM antibody da IgG antibody zuwa SARS-CoV-2 a gwajin magani; ko canjin IgG antibody na SARS-CoV-2 daga mai kyau zuwa mai kyau, ko kuma titer ya karu ≥4 sau a cikin farfadowa fiye da a cikin farfadowa.
