Bangladesh ta ba da rahoton sabbin mutuwar biyar sakamakon COVID-19, mafi girma a kowace rana
A jiya, Bangladesh ta tabbatar da wasu mutane biyar da suka mutu sakamakon COVID-19 a ranar.
Wannan shi ne adadin mutuwar da aka samu a rana daya saboda cutar.
A jiya, Cibiyar Kula da Cututtuka, Kula da Cututtuka da Bincike ta Bangladesh (IEDCR) ta ba da rahoton cewa adadin mutanen da aka rubuta da cutar sun haɗa da mutane 114 da ke aiki da kuma mutane 33 da suka warke waɗanda ke zaune a gida.
An samu mutuwar mutane 17 a duniya.
A wani taron labarai na kan layi, darektan IEDCR, Dokta Meerjady Sabrina Flora, ta ce wadanda suka mutu sun hada da maza hudu da mace daya.
A cewar Dr. Meerjady, mutane biyu sun wuce shekaru 60, biyu sun kasance tsakanin shekaru 51 zuwa 60, ɗayan kuma yana da shekaru 41 zuwa 50.
Ta kuma ce biyu daga cikin wadanda aka kashe sun fito ne daga Dhaka.
Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya (WHO) ta ayyana COVID-19 a matsayin annoba a ranar 11 ga Maris.
Wani jami'in asibiti ya shaida wa Anadolu Agency, wata jaridar labarai ta gida, cewa daya daga cikin wadanda suka mutu shi ne Jalal Saifur Rahman, darektan Hukumar yaki da cin hanci da rashawa ta Bengal, wanda aka kula da shi a asibitin Kuwait Maitree.
A ranar Asabar, a cikin wani bidiyo na kan layi, Ministan Sufuri da Bridges na Bangladesh Obaidul Quader ya ce za a rufe sufurin jama'a na tsawon lokaci fiye da yadda aka shirya, har zuwa wannan Asabar mai zuwa.
Wannan rufewar jigilar jama'a ta fara ne a ranar 26 ga Maris kuma an shirya ta ƙare a ranar Asabar, 4 ga Afrilu.
Har ila yau, ana ba da izinin jigilar kayayyakin da ake bukata, wato, magani, mai da abinci.
Labaran farko na kamuwa da cutar COVID-19 a Bangladesh sun kasance a ranar 8 ga Maris, a cikin mutane biyu da suka dawo daga Italiya da kuma matar ɗaya daga cikinsu.
A ranar 19 ga Maris, waɗannan ukun sun riga sun warke.
SARS-CoV-2 ya wuce kamuwa da cuta miliyan ɗaya a duniya
A ranar Alhamis, jimlar adadin masu kamuwa da cutar SARS-CoV-2 ta wuce miliyan ɗaya a duk duniya, bayanan Jami'ar Johns Hopkins sun nuna.
Akalla mutuwar dubu 52 an danganta su da COVID-19, cutar da coronavirus ta haifar.
Wannan muhimmin abu ya faru a ranar da Malawi ta tabbatar da kamuwa da cutar coronavirus ta farko kuma Zambia ta sami mutuwar farko da ta shafi coronavirus.
Koriya ta Arewa ta ce, a ranar Alhamis, ita ce ɗaya daga cikin ƙasashe kalilan da suka rage ba tare da kamuwa da cutar coronavirus ba.
A jiya, Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya ta ba da rahoton mutane 1,051,635 da aka tabbatar da cutar, ciki har da mutane 79,332 a cikin sa'o'i ashirin da huɗu kafin karfe 10 na safe na ranar 4 ga Afrilu, a lokacin Turai ta Tsakiya (0800 UTC).
A Amurka, an yi rikodin sama da mutane dubu 244 da suka kamu da cutar coronavirus, wanda ya danganta da mutuwar akalla 5,900.
Labarin CBS News, yana ambaton bayanan Jami'ar Johns Hopkins, akwai mutuwar Amurka sama da 1,000 a ranar Laraba sakamakon kamuwa da cutar coronavirus.
A faɗin duniya, ƙasashe sun sanar da tsauraran matakai don hana cutar yaduwa.
A ranar Alhamis, magajin garin Moscow Sergei Sobyanin ya tsawaita dokar kulle a birnin har zuwa 1 ga watan Mayu.
A kasa, Shugaba Vladimir Putin ya bayyana cewa za a ci gaba da biyan 'yan Rasha ba tare da su je aiki ba har zuwa 30 ga Afrilu.
