Saudiyya ta tsawaita dokar hana fita a cikin biranen Makka da Madina don tsawon yini; a baya, dokar ta fita tana aiki ne kawai tsakanin 3 na yamma da 6 na safe.
Thailand ta shirya aiwatar da dokar hana fita tsakanin 10 na yamma da 4 na safe.
Gwamnan Ohio, Mike DeWine, ya sanar da cewa jihar ta tsawaita dokar zama a gida har zuwa 1 ga Mayu.
Shaguna a Ostiraliya sun rage iyakar takardar wanka ta kowace ma'amala
A ranar Lahadi da Asabar da yamma, shagunan sayar da kayayyaki na Australiya Woolworths da Coles sun rage ƙuntatawa kan sayen takardar wanka zuwa biyu da ɗaya kunshin a kowace ma'amala a duk shagunan a matakin ƙasa, bi da bi.
