Ayyukan da ke cikin dakin gawa masu haɗarin haɗari sun haɗa da ma'aikata da ke aiki wajen shirya gawarwakin mutanen da suka san ko kuma ake zargin cewa suna da cutar COVID-19 a lokacin mutuwarsu; waɗannan suna zama haɗarin haɗari sosai idan suka yi aikin gawa. Ƙarin aikin injiniya don waɗannan rukunin haɗarin sun haɗa da ɗakunan keɓewa don marasa lafiya da aka sani ko ake zargin COVID-19, gami da lokacin da ake gudanar da hanyoyin samar da sinadarai.
Ƙarfafa iska mai ƙarancin matsa lamba na musamman na iya zama da kyau a wasu wuraren kiwon lafiya da kuma gawawwaki.
Ya kamata a bi da samfurori da matakan tsaro na Biosafety Level 3.
Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya (WHO) ta ba da shawarar cewa a raba marasa lafiya masu shigowa zuwa wuraren jiran daban-daban dangane da ko suna da zargin COVID-19. Baya ga sauran PPE, OSHA ta ba da shawarar masu numfashi ga waɗanda ke aiki a cikin ƙafa 6 na marasa lafiya da aka sani, ko ake zargin suna da cutar SARS-CoV-2, da waɗanda ke yin hanyoyin samar da aerosol.
A Amurka, dole ne a yi amfani da N95 mai tace fuska mai tsabta da aka amince da shi ta NIOSH ko kuma mafi kyau a cikin tsarin cikakken shirin kariya na numfashi da ya ƙunshi gwajin dacewa, horo, da kuma jarrabawar likita.
Sauran nau'ikan kayan numfashi na iya samar da kariya mai yawa da inganta kwanciyar hankali ga ma'aikata. WHO ba ta ba da shawarar rufe tufafi ba, saboda COVID-19 cuta ce ta hanyar numfashi maimakon ta hanyar ruwan jiki.
Hukumar ta WHO ta ba da shawarar yin amfani da abin rufe fuska na tiyata kawai ga ma'aikatan binciken da ke wurin shiga.
Ga waɗanda ke tattara samfurin numfashi daga, kula da, ko jigilar marasa lafiya na COVID-19 ba tare da wani aikin samar da aerosol ba, WHO ta ba da shawarar yin amfani da abin rufe fuska na tiyata, tabarau, ko garkuwa, rigar, da safofin hannu.
Idan an yi aikin samar da aerosol, an maye gurbin abin rufe fuska na tiyata da na numfashi na N95 ko FFP2.
Ganin cewa wadatar PPE a duniya bai isa ba, WHO ta ba da shawarar rage buƙatar PPE ta hanyar telemedicine, shinge na zahiri kamar windows masu tsabta, ba da izinin waɗanda ke cikin kulawa kai tsaye kawai su shiga daki tare da mai haƙuri na COVID-19, ta amfani da PPE kawai da ake buƙata don takamaiman aikin, ci gaba da amfani da na'urar numfashi iri ɗaya ba tare da cire ta ba yayin kula da marasa lafiya da yawa tare da ganewar asali iri ɗaya, saka idanu da daidaita sarkar samar da PPE, da hana amfani da masks ga mutanen da ba su da alamun bayyanar cututtuka.
