b' Angiotensin- mai canza enzyme 2 (ACE2) wani enzyme ne da aka haɗa zuwa farfajiyar waje (ƙwayoyin sel) na ƙwayoyin a cikin huhu, jijiyoyi, zuciya, koda, da hanji.
ACE2 yana hana aikin enzymes da ke canza angiotensin (ACE) ta hanyar rage adadin angiotensin-II da haɓaka Ang(1-7) yana mai da shi kyakkyawan magani don magance cututtukan zuciya.ACE2 kuma yana aiki a matsayin hanyar shiga cikin sel don wasu ƙwayoyin coronaviruses.
Ana kiran sigar mutum na enzyme hACE2.
Angiotensin- mai canza enzyme 2 wani zinc ne wanda ya ƙunshi metalloenzyme wanda ke located a farfajiya na endothelial da sauran kwayoyin.
Protein ACE2 ya ƙunshi yankin N-terminal peptidase M2 da kuma yankin C-terminal collectrin renal amino acid transporter.
ACE2 shine furotin membrane mai wucewa guda ɗaya na nau'in I, tare da yankin enzymatically mai aiki a farfajiya na ƙwayoyin a cikin huhu da sauran kayan.
Ƙaramar ƙwayoyin halitta na ACE2 ta rabu da yankin transmembrane ta wani enzyme da aka sani da sheddase, kuma an saki furotin mai narkewa a cikin jini kuma a ƙarshe an fitar da shi cikin fitsari.
ACE2 yana cikin mafi yawan kwayoyin: ACE2 yana haɗe da membrane na ƙwayoyin cuta na ƙwayoyin cuta na huhu na II, ƙwayoyin enterocytes na ƙananan hanji, ƙwayoyin endothelial na jijiyoyin jini da na jini da ƙwayoyin jijiyoyin jini a mafi yawan kwayoyin.
Hakanan ana samun bayyanar ACE2 mRNA a cikin ƙwaƙwalwar ƙwaƙwalwa, striatum, hypothalamus, da ƙwaƙwalwar ƙwaƙwalwa.
Babban aikin ACE2 shine ya zama mai daidaitawa ga ACE.
ACE ta raba hormone na angiotensin I zuwa cikin angiotensin II mai hana jini.
ACE2 kuma ya raba carboxyl- terminal amino acid phenylalanine daga angiotensin II (Asp-Arg-Val-Tyr-Ile-His-Pro-Phe) kuma ya hydrolyses shi zuwa vasodilator angiotensin (1-7), (H-Asp-Arg-Val-Tyr-Ile-His-Pro-OH).
ACE2 kuma zai iya raba wasu wasu peptides ciki har da [des-Arg9]-bradykinin, apelin, neurotensin, dynorphin A, da ghrelin.
ACE2 kuma yana daidaita safarar membrane na mai ɗaukar amino acid SLC6A19 kuma an haɗa shi da cutar Hartnup.
A matsayin furotin na transmembrane, ACE2 yana aiki a matsayin babban wurin shiga cikin sel don wasu ƙwayoyin cuta, gami da HCoV-NL63; SARS-CoV (ƙwayoyin cuta da ke haifar da SARS); da SARS-CoV-2 (ƙwayoyin cuta da ke haifar da COVID-19).
Musamman, ɗaurewar furotin S1 na SARS-CoV da SARS-CoV2 zuwa yankin enzymatic na ACE2 a saman sel yana haifar da endocytosis da kuma canzawar duka kwayar cutar da enzyme zuwa endosomes da ke cikin sel.
Wannan tsari na shigarwa kuma yana buƙatar ƙaddamar da furotin S ta hanyar protease serine TMPRSS2, wanda a halin yanzu ana binciken hana shi a matsayin magani mai yuwuwa. Wannan ya haifar da wasu su yi tunanin cewa rage matakan ACE2, a cikin kwayoyin halitta, na iya taimakawa wajen yaki da kamuwa da cuta.
Duk da haka, kungiyoyi da hukumomi masu yawa sun bada shawarar ci gaba da maganin ACE da ARB.
